      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering an exceptional E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise mechanical engagement, paired with a factory M-variable differential lock. The chassis is structurally immaculate with proactive subframe reinforcement already completed. The suspension retains its original geometry and damping rates, ensuring the iconic handling profile remains uncompromised. Finished in a deep, swirl-free gloss with no oxidation on the Shadowline trim, this vehicle represents a turn-key opportunity for the discerning enthusiast seeking a pure, naturally aspirated driving experience.",
