    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that defies its age, this car is in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish, protected by a professional ceramic coating; you will find no stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks on its flawless body. Every panel gap is factory-perfect. Inside, the cabin remains a pristine sanctuary. The premium leather seats are supple, showing zero signs of creasing or bolster wear, and still carry that distinct new-car aroma. The dashboard, trim, and buttons are free of any fading or tactile wear, functioning with the crisp precision of a new vehicle. Mechanically, this car has been pampered with an open-checkbook maintenance philosophy. It has been exclusively serviced at authorized centers, and the engine bay is remarkably clean, showing no signs of fluid leaks or heat-related aging. It drives tightly and quietly, exactly as the engineers intended. This sale includes all original keys, a complete set of stamped service manuals, and the original window sticker. For the buyer seeking a 'no-excuses' example, this is the one.",
